<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In Option section within Zend_View reference guide chapter it was defined that the default value for the <em>encoding</em> property is <em>ISO-8859-1</em>. However, in the Zend\View\Abstract.php class in line 115 the default value is <em>UTF-8</em>.</p>

